46
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:16,520
l couldn't go to the movíes
or ríde ín an automobíle...

47
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:18,600
.. .or even on a streetcar.

48
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:21,880
And a míllíon other thíngs.

49
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:26,320
But somehow. we chíldren
stíll managed to have fun.

50
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:29,720
Thís morníng.
Father woke me at 5:OO.. .

51
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:33,080
.. .and told me to hurry
and get dressed.

52
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:36,160
We were goíng ínto hídíng.

53
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:39,120
l was to put on
