PETRONELLA: Excuse me, Mr. Frank.
FRANK: Yes?

125
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:29,520
PETRONELLA: Where do you sleep?
FRANK: This room is our bedroom.

126
00:14:29,680 --> 00:14:33,480
Oh, no, no. You take the upstairs.
We'll sleep down here.

127
00:14:33,680 --> 00:14:36,400
l've thought this out.
It's the best arrangement.

128
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:39,160
The only arrangement.

129
00:14:39,360 --> 00:14:42,960
Edith? You must have some rest, dear.

130
