-What are you going to do with it?
-Burn it.

167
00:17:38,520 --> 00:17:41,920
lt's funny,
l don't think l could burn mine.

168
00:17:42,080 --> 00:17:43,840
-l don't know why.
PETER: You couldn't?

169
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:47,040
Something they make you wear
so they can kick you around.

170
00:17:47,240 --> 00:17:50,440
l know. But after all...

171
