No, thanks. This is fine.

175
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:09,080
You won't forget to take off
your shoes, will you?

176
00:18:10,760 --> 00:18:12,960
Peter.. .

177
00:18:13,440 --> 00:18:16,480
...it's nice to have you with us.

178
00:18:17,080 --> 00:18:19,680
Yes, Mr. Frank.

179
00:18:21,280 --> 00:18:23,280
See you later.

180
00:18:24,800 --> 00:18:27,280
Did you know that he went
to the same school that--?

181
