203
00:23:32,480 --> 00:23:36,400
KRALER:
It is us, Miep and Kraler.

204
00:23:41,520 --> 00:23:44,600
FRANK: Good evening, Mr. Kraler.
Good evening, Miep.

205
00:23:45,640 --> 00:23:48,640
KRALER:
Good evening, Annele.

206
00:23:49,920 --> 00:23:51,760
-Oh, Mr. Frank.
-Yes?

207
