Accordíng to hím. nothíng. l repeat.
nothíng. ís ríght about me.

758
01:13:33,080 --> 01:13:35,800
Whíle he was goíng on at me.
l thought:

759
01:13:35,960 --> 01:13:39,920
''Someday. l'm goíng
to gíve you such a smack.. .

760
01:13:40,080 --> 01:13:43,560
...that you'll fly ríght up
to the ceílíng.''

761
01:13:44,560 --> 01:13:50,000
Why ís ít that every grownup thínks
he knows the way to bríng up chíldren?

762
01:13:56,080 --> 01:14:00,080
Partícularly the grownups
that haven't any.

763
01:14:01,960 --> 01:14:05,040
Monday. the 9th of November. 19$2.

764
