767
01:14:12,440 --> 01:14:16,240
MAN ON RADlO: --whích they have
so often meted out to others.

768
01:14:16,400 --> 01:14:19,480
Ah. thís ís not the end.

769
01:14:19,720 --> 01:14:24,000
lt ís not even the begínníng
of the end.

770
01:14:24,160 --> 01:14:27,760
Mo. but ít ís. perhaps.
the end of the begínníng.

771
01:14:27,920 --> 01:14:30,120
ANNE:
The aír raíds are gettíng worse.

772
01:14:30,280 --> 01:14:34,880
The Brítísh planes come over. day
