May l have the hats, please?
Thank you.

835
01:19:40,680 --> 01:19:42,080
Very nice, very nice.

836
01:19:42,240 --> 01:19:44,480
-That was very moving.
-lt isn't over yet.

837
01:19:44,640 --> 01:19:46,840
-Sit down!
VAN DAAN: Where are you going?

838
01:19:47,000 --> 01:19:49,560
There's lots more.
Songs and presents.

839
01:19:49,760 --> 01:19:52,040
-Presents?
EDITH: Not this year, unfortunately.

840
01:19:52,200 --> 01:19:55,360
But always on Hannukah,
everyone gives presents. Everyone.

841
01:19:55,560 --> 01:19:57,800
-That's right.
-Like our St. Nicholas Day.

842
01:19:57,960 --> 01:19:59,000
St. Nicholas Day.

843
