Look at that.

883
01:22:19,000 --> 01:22:21,240
Light it! Go on, light it!

884
01:22:23,400 --> 01:22:25,120
lt's tobacco.

885
01:22:25,280 --> 01:22:27,280
Really, it is.

886
01:22:28,080 --> 01:22:31,120
There's a little fluff in it, but not much.

887
01:22:34,280 --> 01:22:35,960
Ah, yes.

888
01:22:36,120 --> 01:22:37,640
[COUGHS]

889
