1067
01:45:27,240 --> 01:45:31,960
But then.
l don't understand her eíther.

1068
01:45:34,600 --> 01:45:37,920
There ís one great change. however.. .

1069
01:45:38,080 --> 01:45:41,040
.. .a change ín myself.

1070
01:45:41,200 --> 01:45:46,440
l read somewhere that gírls of my age
don't feel quíte certaín of themselves.

1071
01:45:46,600 --> 01:45:48,440
That they become quíet wíthín.. .

1072
01:45:48,600 --> 01:45:54,160
...and begín to thínk of the míracle
that ís takíng place ín theír bodíes.

1073
01:45:55,320 --> 01:45:59,320
l thínk that what ís happeníng
